1
00:00:06,176 --> 00:00:08,255
Tonight's guests are important.

2
00:00:08,536 --> 00:00:10,056
Everyone, stay alert.

3
00:00:27,855 --> 00:00:28,655
Sir,

4
00:00:28,815 --> 00:00:30,335
we're not open now.

5
00:00:31,416 --> 00:00:32,375
We've received a report

6
00:00:32,416 --> 00:00:34,096
that Deep In The Bustle

7
00:00:34,495 --> 00:00:36,175
is suspected of harboring
a major criminal.

8
00:00:36,416 --> 00:00:37,495
Cooperate with our search.

9
00:00:38,375 --> 00:00:38,976
Move aside.

10
00:00:39,455 --> 00:00:40,415
Captain Hansi,

11
00:00:41,015 --> 00:00:42,095
how could we

12
00:00:42,095 --> 00:00:43,735
possibly harbor any major criminal?

13
00:00:44,095 --> 00:00:45,015
Did you make a mistake?

14
00:00:49,335 --> 00:00:50,335
Sir,

15
00:00:50,735 --> 00:00:51,936
I want to let you in,

16
00:00:52,316 --> 00:00:52,816
but

17
00:00:52,816 --> 00:00:53,536
it's our duty

18
00:00:53,536 --> 00:00:54,256
to guard

19
00:00:54,256 --> 00:00:55,576
Deep In The Bustle's safety.

20
00:00:56,695 --> 00:00:57,195
Let me

21
00:00:57,695 --> 00:00:59,335
inform Ms. Bai,

22
00:00:59,375 --> 00:01:00,015
okay?

23
00:01:02,616 --> 00:01:03,176
Hurry up.

24
00:01:03,375 --> 00:01:04,415
Don't hinder us.

25
00:01:13,256 --> 00:01:14,176
Hello, Mr. Nie.

26
00:01:14,495 --> 00:01:16,055
Chief Zheng
from Changqingtai Police Bureau

27
00:01:16,055 --> 00:01:17,135
has taken his team there.

28
00:01:17,335 --> 00:01:18,456
How long until you arrive?

29
00:01:19,016 --> 00:01:20,495
The timing should be perfect.

30
00:01:20,976 --> 00:01:21,736
Remember this.

31
00:01:21,855 --> 00:01:23,215
Don't mess up the act.

32
00:01:23,656 --> 00:01:25,495
Play with the mouse slowly
to make it fun.

33
00:01:26,456 --> 00:01:28,256
Don't worry, Mr. Nie.

34
00:01:29,335 --> 00:01:30,096
This time,

35
00:01:30,135 --> 00:01:32,096
I'll make it flawless,

36
00:01:32,335 --> 00:01:33,456
making Chief Zheng

37
00:01:33,976 --> 00:01:35,256
helpless,

38
00:01:35,456 --> 00:01:37,376
fully demonstrating my authority

39
00:01:37,656 --> 00:01:39,256
as the Cabinet Special Envoy.

40
00:01:39,415 --> 00:01:40,295
Good.

41
00:01:48,415 --> 00:01:49,695
Everything's arranged.

42
00:01:50,256 --> 00:01:51,096
Next,

43
00:01:51,096 --> 00:01:53,135
arrange Tang Niansong.

44
00:01:59,536 --> 00:02:00,736
Where were you in the song?

45
00:02:01,896 --> 00:02:02,456
Mr. Nie...

46
00:02:02,575 --> 00:02:03,256
Never mind.

47
00:02:04,096 --> 00:02:04,976
Then we'll

48
00:02:05,775 --> 00:02:09,976
start from the beginning.

49
00:02:10,946 --> 00:02:13,216
=The Glory Fades=

50
00:02:14,016 --> 00:02:16,320
=Episode 27=
(Besieged on All Sides)

51
00:02:16,895 --> 00:02:18,295
Tang is quite something.

52
00:02:18,976 --> 00:02:20,575
We came all this way for him,

53
00:02:20,816 --> 00:02:21,976
yet he's hiding from us.

54
00:02:22,615 --> 00:02:23,816
But there's one thing

55
00:02:23,816 --> 00:02:25,336
I think Secretary Liu was right.

56
00:02:26,135 --> 00:02:27,096
Tang

57
00:02:27,216 --> 00:02:28,536
must've really run into trouble.

58
00:02:29,376 --> 00:02:30,295
And this trouble

59
00:02:30,615 --> 00:02:31,976
is beyond his ability to solve.

60
00:02:33,216 --> 00:02:34,135
Or to put it bluntly,

61
00:02:34,656 --> 00:02:35,615
that phone call

62
00:02:35,816 --> 00:02:36,936
can finish him.

63
00:02:37,615 --> 00:02:38,855
Tang is meticulous.

64
00:02:39,096 --> 00:02:40,295
What could take him down

65
00:02:40,936 --> 00:02:42,056
must be above Cabinet level.

66
00:02:47,496 --> 00:02:49,216
It's an ulterior motive.

67
00:02:53,295 --> 00:02:54,455
Chief,

68
00:02:54,895 --> 00:02:56,496
what brings you here?

69
00:02:56,496 --> 00:02:57,615
With such a large operation,

70
00:02:58,175 --> 00:02:59,776
is there a special mission?

71
00:03:00,096 --> 00:03:01,096
Ms. Bai,

72
00:03:01,735 --> 00:03:03,455
what's going on with you people?

73
00:03:04,135 --> 00:03:04,855
What...

74
00:03:05,656 --> 00:03:06,455
What have we done?

75
00:03:07,096 --> 00:03:08,415
We received public tip-off.

76
00:03:08,575 --> 00:03:10,096
Deep In The Bustle

77
00:03:10,096 --> 00:03:12,936
is suspected of harboring suspects
from the chemical plant explosion.

78
00:03:13,855 --> 00:03:14,656
All units.

79
00:03:15,295 --> 00:03:17,695
Seal all entrances.
Search the place thoroughly.

80
00:03:17,695 --> 00:03:19,295
Especially the underground areas.

81
00:03:19,496 --> 00:03:20,096
You must

82
00:03:20,135 --> 00:03:21,135
locate the suspects.

83
00:03:21,455 --> 00:03:21,955
Yes, sir.

84
00:03:26,376 --> 00:03:27,376
Chief Zheng,

85
00:03:27,776 --> 00:03:29,415
what is this all about?

86
00:03:35,855 --> 00:03:36,656
Ms. Bai,

87
00:03:37,376 --> 00:03:38,455
I have no choice.

88
00:03:39,216 --> 00:03:40,256
Orders from higher-ups.

89
00:03:41,656 --> 00:03:42,536
From the state?

90
00:03:43,256 --> 00:03:44,056
Even higher up.

91
00:03:45,776 --> 00:03:46,895
The Cabinet.

92
00:03:49,135 --> 00:03:50,936
Was alerting
such high authorities necessary?

93
00:03:51,855 --> 00:03:53,096
Right.

94
00:03:53,615 --> 00:03:54,455
Everyone knows

95
00:03:54,656 --> 00:03:56,015
what happened when Chief Phachai

96
00:03:56,015 --> 00:03:57,415
caused trouble here

97
00:03:57,455 --> 00:03:58,256
ten years ago.

98
00:03:58,976 --> 00:03:59,496
To this day,

99
00:03:59,496 --> 00:04:00,776
he's still in prison.

100
00:04:02,615 --> 00:04:03,415
Ms. Bai,

101
00:04:03,976 --> 00:04:05,216
I'm forced to do this.

102
00:04:06,496 --> 00:04:07,336
Today,

103
00:04:07,496 --> 00:04:08,615
I have to offend you.

104
00:04:09,855 --> 00:04:10,656
Wait a moment.

105
00:04:10,695 --> 00:04:11,496
Let me make a call.

106
00:04:27,776 --> 00:04:28,615
Ms. Bai,

107
00:04:28,855 --> 00:04:30,456
long time no see.

108
00:04:31,855 --> 00:04:32,815
Deputy Mayor He.

109
00:04:34,016 --> 00:04:34,815
Now,

110
00:04:35,136 --> 00:04:36,696
you should be Special Envoy He.

111
00:04:45,656 --> 00:04:47,935
I don't have access to this room either.

112
00:04:48,855 --> 00:04:49,855
We can only wait

113
00:04:50,096 --> 00:04:51,656
until Mr. Tu returns to enter.

114
00:04:53,295 --> 00:04:53,896
I do.

115
00:05:00,016 --> 00:05:01,255
May I ask how could

116
00:05:02,216 --> 00:05:02,815
you have

117
00:05:02,815 --> 00:05:03,615
Deep In The Bustle

118
00:05:03,615 --> 00:05:04,935
founder's wristband?

119
00:05:06,055 --> 00:05:06,656
Then let

120
00:05:06,656 --> 00:05:08,815
Chief Zheng who handles An Ruoxi's case

121
00:05:08,815 --> 00:05:09,855
answer for me.

122
00:05:10,815 --> 00:05:12,096
You weren't aware, Ms. Bai?

123
00:05:12,295 --> 00:05:13,255
This wristband

124
00:05:13,255 --> 00:05:15,495
was found at An Ruoxi's murder scene.

125
00:05:17,855 --> 00:05:18,776
The scene?

126
00:05:57,216 --> 00:05:58,855
I'm He Mike,

127
00:05:59,175 --> 00:06:00,415
Cabinet-appointed leader

128
00:06:00,415 --> 00:06:02,295
of the chemical plant explosion

129
00:06:02,295 --> 00:06:03,175
task force.

130
00:06:03,815 --> 00:06:05,055
Are you Bai Ruxue?

131
00:06:07,855 --> 00:06:08,656
That's me.

132
00:06:08,776 --> 00:06:09,495
Chief Zheng,

133
00:06:09,656 --> 00:06:10,295
take her away.

134
00:06:10,336 --> 00:06:10,836
Yes.

135
00:06:10,896 --> 00:06:11,696
Chief Zheng,

136
00:06:13,175 --> 00:06:14,415
you can't arrest her.

137
00:06:15,495 --> 00:06:16,935
- She's Mr. Tu's...
- Ms. Bai,

138
00:06:18,776 --> 00:06:20,096
we have no choice.

139
00:06:20,896 --> 00:06:21,896
Orders from higher-ups.

140
00:06:38,815 --> 00:06:39,735
Hello, Manni.

141
00:06:41,495 --> 00:06:42,415
Who's leading the team?

142
00:06:44,855 --> 00:06:45,656
Hold them off.

143
00:06:45,815 --> 00:06:46,615
We're heading back.

144
00:06:47,696 --> 00:06:48,495
Drive faster.

145
00:06:50,175 --> 00:06:50,976
Trouble at home.

146
00:06:51,855 --> 00:06:53,016
Bai Ruxue's been taken?

147
00:06:54,375 --> 00:06:54,976
Who?

148
00:06:56,225 --> 00:06:58,784
(Jiasheng, the game officially starts.)

149
00:07:00,776 --> 00:07:02,016
Feng's handwriting.

150
00:07:03,855 --> 00:07:05,415
He Mike dares to pull this stunt.

151
00:07:07,175 --> 00:07:08,656
Director Lin

152
00:07:09,415 --> 00:07:10,536
openly stiles our turf.

153
00:07:11,375 --> 00:07:12,175
Tang Niansong

154
00:07:12,896 --> 00:07:14,375
vanished during the banquet.

155
00:07:15,216 --> 00:07:15,815
And today,

156
00:07:17,175 --> 00:07:18,615
they openly snatched Bai Ruxue.

157
00:07:21,295 --> 00:07:22,216
I don't understand.

158
00:07:22,896 --> 00:07:24,216
His father's been critically ill,

159
00:07:24,216 --> 00:07:25,136
yet he never returned.

160
00:07:25,136 --> 00:07:26,175
Beyond reconciliation,

161
00:07:26,175 --> 00:07:27,576
there's no extra phone call.

162
00:07:28,255 --> 00:07:29,175
What is his reason?

163
00:07:29,295 --> 00:07:30,096
For money.

164
00:07:30,656 --> 00:07:31,375
Money?

165
00:07:31,815 --> 00:07:32,815
Do we lack money?

166
00:07:32,935 --> 00:07:34,255
Who hates more money?

167
00:07:47,255 --> 00:07:48,055
Jiasheng,

168
00:07:48,735 --> 00:07:50,175
just tell me directly.

169
00:07:50,935 --> 00:07:53,136
What happened between you two?

170
00:08:24,776 --> 00:08:25,855
That was three years ago.

171
00:08:26,896 --> 00:08:28,495
Qin Wei secured a deal.

172
00:08:29,255 --> 00:08:30,055
During those days,

173
00:08:30,216 --> 00:08:31,175
I was tied up.

174
00:08:31,855 --> 00:08:32,976
Ruoxi went in my place.

175
00:08:36,935 --> 00:08:38,336
Come on, let's have a drink.

176
00:08:38,696 --> 00:08:39,495
Well.

177
00:08:40,296 --> 00:08:41,056
Here's to us,

178
00:08:41,255 --> 00:08:43,416
collaborating on endeavors,
and sharing achievements.

179
00:08:43,416 --> 00:08:44,015
Cheers!

180
00:08:44,015 --> 00:08:45,015
- Come on, cheers!
- Cheers!

181
00:08:45,336 --> 00:08:46,015
Cheers!

182
00:08:55,495 --> 00:08:56,655
Keep them entertained

183
00:08:56,655 --> 00:08:57,336
properly.

184
00:08:57,655 --> 00:08:58,375
See you later.

185
00:08:58,456 --> 00:08:59,255
I'll return soon.

186
00:08:59,816 --> 00:09:00,855
Come on, let's drink.

187
00:09:02,816 --> 00:09:04,015
Mr. Qin.

188
00:09:04,615 --> 00:09:05,255
Darling,

189
00:09:05,615 --> 00:09:06,816
so beautiful.

190
00:09:15,895 --> 00:09:16,735
What are you doing?

191
00:09:19,216 --> 00:09:19,936
Qin Wei,

192
00:09:20,495 --> 00:09:21,615
don't do this deal.

193
00:09:22,096 --> 00:09:23,216
You met today,

194
00:09:23,816 --> 00:09:25,015
but cold-shoulder them.

195
00:09:25,495 --> 00:09:26,416
Let it fade away.

196
00:09:31,135 --> 00:09:31,976
An Ruoxi,

197
00:09:32,535 --> 00:09:34,015
are you out of your mind?

198
00:09:35,096 --> 00:09:36,015
Do you realize

199
00:09:36,655 --> 00:09:38,336
if this deal succeeds,

200
00:09:38,895 --> 00:09:40,216
how much money we could make?

201
00:09:40,296 --> 00:09:41,816
Is money all you care about?

202
00:09:42,696 --> 00:09:44,296
Do you know who gets life sentences

203
00:09:44,296 --> 00:09:45,176
or death penalties?

204
00:09:46,015 --> 00:09:47,096
Murderers, arsonists,

205
00:09:47,096 --> 00:09:48,296
killers for hire,

206
00:09:48,296 --> 00:09:50,375
human traffickers,
and drug producers and dealers.

207
00:09:50,375 --> 00:09:51,816
Showing them mercy

208
00:09:52,615 --> 00:09:54,416
is setting the tigers free.

209
00:09:55,015 --> 00:09:56,015
If this goes on,

210
00:09:56,216 --> 00:09:57,696
it won't just endanger some of us,

211
00:09:58,176 --> 00:09:58,976
but the society,

212
00:09:58,976 --> 00:10:00,895
even the entire country
could also be ruined.

213
00:10:01,775 --> 00:10:02,576
No way.

214
00:10:03,015 --> 00:10:04,015
Absolutely not.

215
00:10:10,416 --> 00:10:11,416
An Ruoxi,

216
00:10:11,576 --> 00:10:13,216
you're hilarious.

217
00:10:14,015 --> 00:10:15,936
Do you really see yourself as Madam?

218
00:10:16,855 --> 00:10:17,456
No,

219
00:10:18,216 --> 00:10:20,216
I think you see yourself as the boss.

220
00:10:21,176 --> 00:10:23,775
Don't lecture me about society
or the country.

221
00:10:25,176 --> 00:10:26,615
If you're so capable,

222
00:10:27,416 --> 00:10:28,976
why don't you join the Cabinet?

223
00:10:30,936 --> 00:10:32,176
I'm telling you,

224
00:10:33,096 --> 00:10:35,816
know your place.

225
00:10:36,336 --> 00:10:38,816
You're just a slut
at Deep In The Bustle.

226
00:10:39,735 --> 00:10:41,735
Even if I gave you a few fancy feathers,

227
00:10:41,816 --> 00:10:44,416
you'd never turn into a phoenix.

228
00:10:44,596 --> 00:10:45,096
You...

229
00:10:45,096 --> 00:10:45,775
What about me?

230
00:10:46,456 --> 00:10:47,456
I'll say it again.

231
00:10:48,176 --> 00:10:49,495
Even if you report this,

232
00:10:49,495 --> 00:10:50,816
Mr. Tu won't agree to it either.

233
00:10:52,495 --> 00:10:53,255
Is that so?

234
00:10:53,336 --> 00:10:55,096
Your pillow talk works wonders, huh?

235
00:10:55,456 --> 00:10:56,895
He does whatever you say?

236
00:10:57,135 --> 00:10:57,936
Alright.

237
00:10:58,696 --> 00:10:59,696
We have got Feng.

238
00:11:00,015 --> 00:11:00,895
If you're capable,

239
00:11:00,976 --> 00:11:01,976
go sleep with Feng too.

240
00:11:01,976 --> 00:11:02,895
Then I'll respect you.

241
00:11:05,416 --> 00:11:06,375
Slut.

242
00:11:07,576 --> 00:11:08,375
You...

243
00:11:33,655 --> 00:11:34,495
Apologize.

244
00:11:35,375 --> 00:11:35,936
Jiasheng,

245
00:11:35,936 --> 00:11:36,735
you want me to...

246
00:11:51,696 --> 00:11:52,696
I'm sorry.

247
00:11:59,576 --> 00:12:01,135
I'm sorry, An Ruoxi.

248
00:12:01,375 --> 00:12:02,895
I was wrong.

249
00:12:03,015 --> 00:12:05,015
Please don't hold it against me.

250
00:12:05,216 --> 00:12:06,336
Alright, Jiasheng.

251
00:12:06,735 --> 00:12:08,135
The apology isn't the point.

252
00:12:08,535 --> 00:12:09,375
What's important

253
00:12:09,375 --> 00:12:10,495
is to think this carefully.

254
00:12:10,535 --> 00:12:11,576
We won't do it.

255
00:12:16,216 --> 00:12:17,296
Didn't hear me?

256
00:12:17,416 --> 00:12:18,096
I said that

257
00:12:18,535 --> 00:12:19,816
we won't do it.

258
00:12:30,096 --> 00:12:30,696
Fine.

259
00:12:31,535 --> 00:12:32,456
I see.

260
00:12:39,816 --> 00:12:41,664
You didn't need
to pressure Qin Wei like that.

261
00:12:42,096 --> 00:12:43,416
He is one of your buddies.

262
00:12:44,296 --> 00:12:45,655
He kept pushing his luck,

263
00:12:45,655 --> 00:12:46,615
yet you defended him.

264
00:12:47,976 --> 00:12:50,015
He'll probably report
to Feng immediately.

265
00:12:50,895 --> 00:12:52,255
Hope Feng doesn't side with him.

266
00:12:59,535 --> 00:13:00,336
Don't worry.

267
00:13:01,176 --> 00:13:03,096
Feng is a man with principles.

268
00:13:04,216 --> 00:13:05,495
He won't earn such money.

269
00:13:06,096 --> 00:13:06,655
Relax.

270
00:13:17,255 --> 00:13:18,015
Head upstairs.

271
00:13:27,655 --> 00:13:28,495
Hello, Feng.

272
00:13:28,816 --> 00:13:29,615
Jiasheng,

273
00:13:30,135 --> 00:13:31,216
feeling confident now?

274
00:13:33,775 --> 00:13:35,096
Qin Wei called you?

275
00:13:38,296 --> 00:13:38,936
Feng,

276
00:13:39,696 --> 00:13:40,615
here is the case.

277
00:13:40,936 --> 00:13:41,696
we can't

278
00:13:41,816 --> 00:13:42,816
make this kind of money.

279
00:13:43,176 --> 00:13:44,495
Once this deal goes through,

280
00:13:44,495 --> 00:13:45,735
those we let go will earn back

281
00:13:45,735 --> 00:13:47,015
their spent money a hundred,

282
00:13:47,015 --> 00:13:49,096
a thousand times over.

283
00:13:49,336 --> 00:13:50,576
Think about who they are.

284
00:13:50,696 --> 00:13:52,936
Murderers and arsonists
who are capable of any atrocity.

285
00:13:52,936 --> 00:13:54,576
It might seem unrelated to us,

286
00:13:54,895 --> 00:13:55,615
but

287
00:13:55,855 --> 00:13:57,296
we all live under the same system.

288
00:13:57,495 --> 00:13:58,976
It will inevitably come back to us.

289
00:13:59,576 --> 00:14:00,535
Well done.

290
00:14:00,976 --> 00:14:03,176
These years when I've been away,
you've grown,

291
00:14:03,416 --> 00:14:05,615
spouting lots of principles.

292
00:14:06,895 --> 00:14:07,576
Feng,

293
00:14:07,855 --> 00:14:08,775
don't misunderstand.

294
00:14:08,895 --> 00:14:09,655
No matter what,

295
00:14:10,216 --> 00:14:11,015
the three of us

296
00:14:11,015 --> 00:14:12,735
are sworn brothers who bowed together.

297
00:14:13,096 --> 00:14:14,495
That's enough to hear that.

298
00:14:14,895 --> 00:14:15,976
I'm your brother.

299
00:14:15,976 --> 00:14:17,056
Then listen to me.

300
00:14:17,296 --> 00:14:18,296
We'll

301
00:14:18,655 --> 00:14:19,416
take it.

302
00:14:20,976 --> 00:14:21,615
Feng.

303
00:14:28,576 --> 00:14:31,981
The number you have dialed
is powered off.

304
00:14:32,064 --> 00:14:34,690
Sorry, the number you have dialed...

305
00:14:48,696 --> 00:14:49,696
I remember this incident.

306
00:14:50,495 --> 00:14:51,816
At that time, Qin Wei threatened

307
00:14:51,816 --> 00:14:53,056
to revenge against Ruoxi.

308
00:14:55,535 --> 00:14:56,375
He's

309
00:14:57,176 --> 00:14:57,936
deranged.

310
00:15:02,495 --> 00:15:04,375
You mean Ruoxi's incident?

311
00:15:12,576 --> 00:15:15,712
No wonder at the abandoned factory,
you wanted to deal with him personally.

312
00:15:15,855 --> 00:15:16,615
He deserved to die.

313
00:15:17,056 --> 00:15:19,255
Death couldn't absolve his guilt.

314
00:15:22,576 --> 00:15:23,655
In the end,

315
00:15:24,336 --> 00:15:25,456
he didn't admit it.

316
00:15:27,176 --> 00:15:28,255
He'd never admit it.

317
00:15:29,135 --> 00:15:30,416
If he had that courage,

318
00:15:30,576 --> 00:15:32,056
he wouldn't have done vile deeds.

319
00:15:33,535 --> 00:15:34,416
He wouldn't dare.

320
00:15:37,015 --> 00:15:37,895
Who would?

321
00:15:55,775 --> 00:15:56,976
If you put it that way,

322
00:16:01,255 --> 00:16:02,855
it must have been Feng.

323
00:16:32,704 --> 00:16:36,378
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

324
00:16:36,677 --> 00:16:39,868
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

325
00:16:41,568 --> 00:16:45,321
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

326
00:16:45,870 --> 00:16:48,669
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

327
00:16:50,140 --> 00:16:53,870
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

328
00:16:54,094 --> 00:16:57,591
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

329
00:16:58,990 --> 00:17:02,677
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

330
00:17:03,315 --> 00:17:08,430
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

331
00:17:09,134 --> 00:17:13,268
♪I feel guilty♪

332
00:17:13,838 --> 00:17:17,582
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

333
00:17:18,446 --> 00:17:21,889
♪Even in tears♪

334
00:17:22,638 --> 00:17:26,552
♪It doesn't matter♪

335
00:17:26,734 --> 00:17:30,557
♪We embrace in dreams♪

336
00:17:31,406 --> 00:17:34,844
♪I let down all my defenses♪

337
00:17:36,078 --> 00:17:39,441
♪Though the story has its end♪

338
00:17:40,206 --> 00:17:47,584
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
